data.description: Introducing 4546 South Detroit Ave, Toledo, OH 43614: A Move-In-Ready Home With A Wealth Of Updates. This 3-Bedroom, 1-Bath Property Now Features A Newer Vinyl Fence, Partially Finished Basement With An Additional Living Area, Fresh Paint, New Carpet In The Living Room, And Updated Handrailing. Added Enhancements Include A Back Deck And Sliding Door To The Enclosed Backyard, Offering The Perfect Outdoor Retreat. Situated On A Corner Lot With A Detached Garage, This Home Combines Comfort With Convenience. Don't Miss Out, Schedule Your Visit Now!
